                            <div class="project-create-actions">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-1"></i>
                                    Create project
                                </button>
                                <button type="reset" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">
                                    Reset
                                </button>
                                <div class="project-create-actions__meta">
                                    Pulse will store your in-progress draft locally while you configure the project.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xl-5">
                            <div class="project-create-note">
                                <span class="project-create-note__eyebrow">What happens next</span>
                                <h3 class="project-create-note__title">After creation, the project is ready for detail work</h3>
                                <p class="project-create-note__copy">
                                    Once created, you can move into tracking, ownership updates, milestone progress, forms and execution review without rebuilding the structure.
                                </p>
                                <ul class="project-create-note__list">
                                    <li>The selected roadmap seeds milestones and activities.</li>
                                    <li>Project members become available for milestone and task ownership.</li>
                                    <li>Appearance settings flow into project cards and notifications.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="preview-card d-none mt-3" id="previewCard">
                                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                    <div>
                                        <div class="preview-title" id="previewTitle"></div>
                                        <div class="preview-sub" id="previewOwner"></div>
                                        <div class="preview-sub" id="previewDates"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-end">
                                        <span class="badge-soft" id="previewBadge">
                                            <i class="fas fa-users me-1"></i>
                                            <span id="previewMemberCount">0</span> members
                                        </span>
                                        <div class="mt-1">
                                            <span class="badge-soft">
                                                <i class="fas fa-flag me-1"></i>
                                                <span id="previewMilestoneCount">0</span> milestones
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mt-2 preview-sub" id="previewDescription"></div>
                                <div class="mt-2" id="previewMilestonesList"></div>
                                <div class="mt-2 preview-sub">
                                    Project data is logged to console; send it to backend or pass it to the monitoring page.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
</div>
